    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. It runs great and is totally ready for its next big adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin. I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
