    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering torque through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a recently refreshed suspension geometry and reinforced subframe mounting points to ensure torsional rigidity. Mechanically robust with consistent compression across all cylinders, this car offers the quintessential analog driving experience with the visceral induction note only an S54 can provide.",
