    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes an excellent balance between aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor, typical road peppering on the front fascia that is consistent with regular, careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seating remains firm and supportive with only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, featuring a complete service log that highlights recent brake pad replacements and a fresh synthetic oil change. The engine idles smoothly and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. Riding on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining, this car is fully prepared for the road and requires no immediate investment. It is a reliable, well-cared-for example that offers a premium driving experience.",
