    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! Honestly, she\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road and is still in really wonderful shape. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and everything is running just like it should. It\u2019s a super comfy ride that's perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. I\u2019m looking for a good home for it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love driving it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
