      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E36 M3 featuring the S50 3.0L inline-six with single-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers linear power delivery mated to a precise ZF 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec 3.15 limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed subframe bushings, maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator, and the VANOS unit is quiet. It\u2019s a turn-key performance machine ready for the canyons.",
